text: The EPA should not make electricity and everyday products more expensive and should withdraw this new rule.
Americans have seen their wages stagnate and rules like this one increase their electric bills and the cost of everyday products.
Americans are already making smart environmental choices and don’t need the EPA making new rules for their lives.
Yesterday, President Obama introduced new EPA regulations for electricity plants across the U.S. This rule will increase electricity bills.
